{
  "stem": "1918.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 310.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And cause-- we simply knew nothing, only what Hitler wanted us to know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you know, there are so many questions that are irrelevant because, for instance, having arrived in Auschwitz, and we saw a sign called Auschwitzen, and we had no idea where we were, none whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we never heard anything about the Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We never heard anything about deportations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We never heard anything that Hitler did not want us to know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Therefore, our fear when we heard his incessant ranting and ravings and the Jews, Jews, Jude, Jude, Jude, we knew that it's all against us, and we were terrified.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were living still in our homes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of Europe's Jews were already decimated, and we're still living with Persian rugs in our homes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think it certainly did not have to occupy Hungary, but I think it was Eichmann's last hurrah, and just for good measure, just to get rid of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he needed no excuse for anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He, he needed-- he didn't have to march into Hungary, as far as I could tell.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nonetheless, we were faced with all of this that has-- that the rest of Europe's Jews have already gone through, and have been murdered, and experienced all that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we knew nothing about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were learning every single day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was affecting our lives in an insane way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No, we were not going to school, and we're not going to the store buying a dress.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were-- all we had to do is constantly comply by the onrushing orders that were shouted at us from the newspapers and the radio and the town crier.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There has not been any food for a long time by then because Hitler stole everything from us.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
